\pard\b\f1\fs36\sa280 Quick Troubleshooting\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa120\f0\u8226\tab \b Grainy sauce: \b0 Lower heat; add a splash of cream and whisk. Melt cheese off direct heat.\par
