\pard\fi-360\li720\sa120\f0\u8226\tab \b Dry baked mac: \b0 Stir in 1/2 cup warm milk before topping and baking.\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa120\f0\u8226\tab \b Clumpy cheese: \b0 Add cheese gradually with constant stirring; keep below a simmer.\par
